    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "friend or a professional... i don't know. it doesn't really change the fact that the person who actually made the world feel real is just gone. i'm just staring at the walls and realizing there's nothing left to wait for. what's the point of even trying to \"navigate\" this when the destination is just more of this emptiness?",
