    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "a \"new way to feel real\"? i dont think that's possible. it feels like i'm just an echo of someone else. everything i do—eating, sleeping, working—it's all just empty rituals now. it’s like i’m already gone, and staying here is just making a long, slow exit even harder than it needs to be.",
